Section 1
## Navbar - Fixed Navigation Bar ##
Stays visible as the user scrolls. Contains the MBHTE logo + center name on the left, and five navigation links
(Home, Programs, Locations, Schedule, Login) on the right. Collapses to a hamburger menu on mobile.
Becomes fully opaque on scroll.

Section 2
## First impression. A gold scholarship badge anchors the top, followed by the center name as the main
headline. A subtitle gives the location. Three CTA buttons serve all audiences: Enroll Now (new applicants),
Browse Programs (explorers), and Track Application (returning users). Four stat boxes highlight key figures.
Animated waves flow at the bottom for visual energy.

Section 3
Sectors — Program Categories
6 clickable tiles group all 15 programs by industry sector: ICT, Tourism & Food, Construction, Health,
Agriculture, and Security. Each tile shows an icon, sector name, and program count. Clicking scrolls down to
the Programs section. Helps users quickly find courses relevant to their field.

Section 4
Why Us — Value Proposition
3 benefit cards on the green background address the most common questions from applicants and partner
institutions: Is it free? (100% scholarship), Is it recognized? (TESDA NC certificate), and Is the training quality?
(accredited trainers & facilities). Builds trust before the user reaches the program list.

Section 5
Quick Access — Action Hub
4 shortcut cards for the most common tasks: Online Registration, Track Application, Find Locations, and
Training Schedule. Designed for returning visitors who know what they need and want to get there fast —
without scrolling through the full page.

Section 6
Programs — Course Catalog
A 3-column grid of 15 program cards, each showing a sector icon, course name, training hours, schedule,
location, benefits, and a Pre-Register button. Cards are organized alphabetically. The consistent card layout
makes it easy to scan and compare. Each card links directly to the registration modal.

Section 7
Map — Training Center Locator
An embedded interactive map (loaded via iframe from ccdomap.html) showing TESDA-accredited training
centers across BARMM. Helps general public and walk-in visitors find the nearest center. Especially useful for
users from provinces outside Cotabato City.

Section 8
Calendar — Schedule & Announcements
Two-column layout: left column lists upcoming training schedules with dates, titles, and venue details. Right
column shows important announcements like scholarship application periods, walk-in registration info, and
new center openings. Keeps all audiences — applicants, partners, and the general public — informed without
needing to contact the office.

Section 9
Footer — Contact & Navigation
4-column layout: About (logo + agency description + social links), Quick Links (repeat of key navigation for
accessibility), Contact Us (phone, email, address), and Office Hours (with a "Limited Slots" notice). A copyright
bar closes the page. The logo in the footer reinforces brand identity and institutional credibility.


